	  Or login with <a {{ action 'authenticateWithFacebook' }} class="alert-link" style="cursor: pointer;"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square"></i> Facebook</a> or <a {{ action 'authenticateWithGooglePlus' }} class="alert-link" style="cursor: pointer;"><i class="fa fa-google-plus-square"></i> Google+</a>.
	</div>-->	

</div>
